-- Barcelona Beats Al Sadd 4-0 To Reach Club World Cup Final Against Santos
-- B y   T a r i q   P a n j a
-- 2011-12-15T12:21:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-15/barcelona-beats-al-sadd-4-0-to-reach-club-world-cup-final-against-santos.html
European champion Barcelona beat
Qatar’s Al Sadd 4-0 to reach the final of soccer’s Club World
Cup.  The Spaniards will meet  Brazil ’s Santos in Yokohama,  Japan ,
in three days. Adriano scored two goals, while Seydou Keita and
Maxwell got one each. Striker  David Villa  broke a bone in his
left leg during the first half.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tariq Panja at 
 tpanja@bloomberg.net  